snippet.title: Gunnhildr Game Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
Gunnhildr is a narrative shooter set in a Norse-inspired sci-fi world. Defy the gods and give Niflheim new life through fast paced first person combat in an ever-changing world full of powers and stories to uncover.

Steam link - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1377030/Gunnhildr/
